03/18/76  list_acl, la

Function:  lists the access control lists (ACLs) of files or 
directories.

Syntax:  list_acl


Arguments:
file_name  name of file.
User_ids  access control names of the form Person_id.Project_id.tag.
 If -a, -all, or omitted, entire ACL is listed.


Control arguments:
-all, -a  list entire ACL.
-brief, -bf  suppress message "User name not on ACL of 
 file/directory."
-directory, -dr  list ACL of only directories.
